上海护士四年一次的生日，收到特别的“礼物”。
Shanghai nurses receive a special "gift" for their four-yearly birthdays.
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
查琼芳（第一批上海支援湖北医疗队队员、上海交大医学院附属仁济医院呼吸科主治医师）酒店里的雨伞，在太阳下很和谐。
Cha Qiongfang, a member of the first Shanghai medical team supporting Hubei University, was an umbrella in the Respiratory Department of Yan Chai Hospital, affiliated with the Medical College of Shanghai Jiaotong University.
查琼芳 供图2月29日，支援湖北第三十六天，武汉，晴。
Charg Qiongfang for Figure 29, Support Hubei 36 days, Wuhan, Qing.
今天夜班，所以依旧可以睡到自然醒，可惜生物钟还是在6:30把我唤醒了，刷一会手机，和周医生约好一起去吃早饭。
Today night shift, so can still sleep until the natural wake-up, but the biological clock or at 6: 30 to wake me up, brush a cell phone, and Dr. Chou to have an appointment to have breakfast.
这个时候赶着上八点白班和查房班的伙伴们已经出发，餐厅里空荡荡的。
By this time the day shift at eight o'clock and the squadron had set out, and the dining-room was deserted.
我依旧是牛肉面，人少就可以和师傅提要求了，我提出不加辣不加醋不加葱（昨天加醋的面让我吃的很感性），周医生尝试了武汉热干面，大厨的态度真的很好，我吃面的时候还过来跟我打招呼，说牛肉面的汤有点辣，我连忙表示这点辣我能承受。
I am still beef noodle, few people can and master to ask for, I offered not spicy without vinegar (yesterday vinegar noodles let me eat very sensual), Dr. Zhou tried Wuhan hot-dry noodles, the chef's attitude is really good, I also came to greet me when eating noodles, said beef noodles soup a little spicy, I can quickly express this spicy I can bear.
至于周医生的热干面嘛，我觉得就是上海的冷面，区别一个是冷的，一个是热的，热面里拌了花生酱，周医生没放辣没放醋，跟真正的热干面口味估计打了个大折扣。
As for the hot and dry noodles of Dr. Zhou, I think it is the cold noodles of Shanghai. One is cold and the other is hot. The hot noodles are mixed with peanut butter.
看样子我俩似乎还没熟悉武汉人的最爱啊。
It seems that we are not familiar with Wuhan people's favorite ah.
温暖的阳光从餐厅窗口投射进来，今天是个好天气，看样子我的期盼实现了。
The warm sun shone through the dining-room window. It was a fine day, and it looked as if my expectations had been fulfilled.
酒店的大堂里，撑满了我们雨天用的伞，颜色只有两种，黑色的、黄色的，在阳光下显得特别和谐。
The lobby of the hotel was filled with our rain umbrellas of only two colors, black and yellow, which seemed to be in perfect harmony with the sun.
酒店外面路旁的白玉兰安静地绽放。
White magnolia blossoms quietly on the road outside the hotel.
查琼芳 供图感谢酒店的工作人员默默地为我们提供的服务，感恩每一个为此次抗疫工作默默付出的人们。
Cha Qiongfang diagram to thank the hotel staff silently to provide us with services, grateful for the work of the fight against this silent people.
酒店外面阳光明媚，路旁的白玉兰安静绽放，看到它让我们一扫疲惫。
Outside the hotel sunny, the white magnolia beside the quiet blooming, see it let us sweep tired.
酒店外面马路上的车比前几天多，人行道上依然空无一人，路边的店家无一例外都是铁将军把门，想起去年到武汉时灯火通明热闹非凡的景象，我不禁有些伤感。
Outside the hotel, there are more cars on the road than the previous few days, the sidewalk is still empty, all the shops are invariably iron door, I can not help but think of last year when Wuhan lights up the extraordinary scene, I can not help but feel sad.
从医护群里得知，我们的病人有心理科老师会诊了。
We learned from the medical staff that our patient had been consulted by a psychologist.
金银潭医院有上海支援湖北医疗队中的心理科医生的加盟。
The Gold and Silver Pool Hospital has a team of psychologists from Shanghai to support Hubei Medical Team.
是啊，在重病房，患者住的时间一久，经历了周围人的生死别离，还有家庭所经历的创伤，很多病人出现不同程度的心理问题，有的失眠、有的焦虑，有的抑郁......有一位老年患者因为妻子患新冠肺炎去世，儿子认为他住在医院可以更加安定，不希望病人出院，而病人呢想回家又内心纠结，出现了情绪低落，经过心理科老师的评估后认为他存在中度抑郁，及时对他进行治疗。
Yes, in the heavy ward, the patient lived for a long time, experienced the life and death of those around him, and the trauma experienced by the family. Many of the patients suffered from various psychological problems, some insomnia, some anxiety, some depression...
我们的护士对老先生的照顾已经是无微不至了：不想喝粥，马上递上自己的牛奶饼干；想吃水果，把自己酒店的水果带来给老先生吃。
Our nurses took good care of the old gentleman: they didn't want porridge, they handed in their own milk biscuits, they wanted fruit, they brought their own fruit to the old gentleman.
可是，生活上的照顾远没安抚老人内心深处的问题，看样子我们还需要更多的人文关怀，同时辅以心理老师的帮助。
However, life care far from soothing the elderly heart of the problem, it seems that we still need more humane care, supplemented by psychological teachers.
其实不仅仅是病人，在这么高压的环境下，医护人员也容易出现心理问题，所幸的是我们已经有心理老师加入群体，为一部分人进行心理疏导。
In fact, not only patients, in such a high-pressure environment, medical staff are also prone to psychological problems, fortunately we have psychological teachers to join the group, for some people to conduct psychological counseling.
关于抑郁，想起我们刘组长说的话，就想笑。
As for depression, I want to laugh when I think of what our leader Liu said.
“我否认自己抑郁嘛，你们一定会说我抑郁，因为精神病病人从来不承认自己是精神病。
"I deny that I am depressed. You would say that I am depressed because the mentally ill never admit to being mentally ill.
我承认嘛，你们会说，看，他自己都承认了。
I'll admit it, you'll say, look, he admitted it himself.
”队长助理张明明老师在群里发了一张关于一线医护人员心理测试的问卷，我也上去做了一下，还好，除了中度的心理压力以外，没有抑郁，没有焦虑。
"Assistant captain Zhang Mingming sent out a questionnaire in the group about the psychological tests for front-line medical staff, and I went up to do it, but fortunately there was no depression or anxiety except for moderate psychological stress.
看样子我的心态还不错嘛。
Looks like I'm in a good mood.
今天值夜班，又无缘一场特殊的生日会了，上海市中医院的刘燕护士四年一次的生日今天会在万豪酒店举行，最让人记忆深刻的是大群里发来了刘燕照顾过的病人的祝福视频，看着躺在床上的病人拿下面罩也要表达祝福的时刻，让大家都特别感动。
Nurse Liu Yan's quadrennial birthday will be held today at the Marriott Hotel. What is most impressive is the video from the large group of patients cared for by Liu Yan. We were especially moved to see the patients in bed take off their masks and express their wishes.
我们的付出，换来病人的康复和祝福，这是对我们最大的鼓励和缓压良药。
Our pay, in return for the patient's rehabilitation and blessing, this is our greatest encouragement and gentle pressure medicine.
（澎湃新闻记者 陈斯斯 整理）本期编辑 邢潭推荐阅读。
(Peng Pai journalist Chen Si: This issue editor Xing Tam recommends reading.
